# ── MonoGame Content Pipeline ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Intermediate build artefacts are ignored; the final .xnb files committed to
# Content/ are the pre-built output shipped with the source so "dotnet run"
# works without requiring the mgcb tool to be installed.
Content/obj/
Content/bin/
!Content/*.xnb

